WEBVTT

00:00:00.484 --> 00:00:02.063
Track 10.07

00:00:03.974 --> 00:00:05.187
A: Excuse me.

00:00:06.037 --> 00:00:08.610
B: Yes? How can I help?

00:00:08.860 --> 00:00:11.636
A: What time’s the next train to Eastbourne?

00:00:12.171 --> 00:00:14.581
B: The next train leaves in half an hour.

00:00:14.810 --> 00:00:19.614
A: So at 10:25. Is it a direct train?

00:00:19.912 --> 00:00:22.333
B: No, you change at Brighton.

00:00:22.515 --> 00:00:24.976
A: OK, and which platform is it?

00:00:25.195 --> 00:00:26.669
B: It’s platform 9.

00:00:26.726 --> 00:00:28.619
A: Great! Thanks for your help.

00:00:28.755 --> 00:00:29.844
B: No problem.